one of Boston’s finest vintage &amp; antiques stores, which is called Sams &amp; Son. In my opinion the best address for non-conformist and eclectic things in Boston and MA.</em>\r\n\r\nWhile writing these words, I just realized that both Marco (owner Men vs Machine) and Piere (Sams&amp;Son) are not Boston natives. Maybe there is something about that city that which feels just so right to these guys from the North, not sure. Anyway leave all perceptions about Boston behind and the city will surprise you!', 'Retailer Mikestyle: Statement Store.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '281-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-01 15:07:06', '2016-03-01 15:07:06', '', 281, 'your_website_url_here/2016/03/01/281-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
